PN,31502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781650072
OL,3,CSerena and Venus Williams to play at
OL,4,CWimbledon after getting doubles wild
OL,5,Ccard
OL,7,FThe seven-time Wimbledon singles
OL,8,Fchampion joked on court after the
OL,9,Fvictory that she "had nothing better
OL,10,Fto do" and "got tired of sitting at
OL,11,Fhome", so she decided to return to the
OL,12,Fsport she once dominated.
OL,14,FShe later added that the comeback was
OL,15,Fpartially inspired by the prospect of
OL,16,Fher two daughters, Olympia and Adira,
OL,17,Fbeing able to watch her play.
