PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781650072
OL,3,CSerena and Venus Williams to play at
OL,4,CWimbledon after getting doubles wild
OL,5,Ccard
OL,7,FNeither Serena nor Venus has yet been
OL,8,Fgiven a wild card into the women's
OL,9,Fsingles, although one spot remains
OL,10,Fopen ahead of the Championships, which
OL,11,Fstart on June 29.
OL,13,FSerena appeared to play down rumours
OL,14,Fshe would be making a singles comeback
OL,15,Fwhen the 23-time grand slam champion
OL,16,Fsaid, when quizzed at Queen's, that it
OL,17,Fwas "not my journey right now".
